snippet.title: The Greatest Game Ever Played
snippet.description: Watch a trailer, play golf games, see pictures, get a sports timeline, and download goodies at the official site for the movie starring Shia Lebeouf as Francis Ouimet, the surprise golf champion at the 1913 U. S. Open.

snippet.title: The State of Alaska - An Introduction to the Last Frontier from NETSTATE.COM
snippet.description: In Alaska, the "family car" has wings, vegetables and fruit grow to two times their normal size and moose interrupt golf games when they feel like it.
